@baseUrl = http://localhost:8030
@apiKey = dev-demo-key

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Knowledge query
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/run
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: analyst@contoso.com
X-Role: viewer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_input": "What is our policy on sensitive user lifecycle actions?",
  "context": {
    "channel": "teams"
  }
}

### Action request (non-sensitive)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/run
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: operator@contoso.com
X-Role: operator
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_input": "Create task to review inactive guest users and notify owners",
  "context": {
    "ticket": "INC-9021"
  }
}

### Action request (sensitive, should require admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/run
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: operator@contoso.com
X-Role: operator
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_input": "Disable compromised account and revoke active sessions",
  "context": {
    "ticket": "INC-9022"
  }
}

### Audit log
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflow/audit?limit=20
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-User-Id: admin@contoso.com
X-Role: admin
